            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681381400812-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut 1 large piece of <strong>tin foil </strong>per person, then lay each <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>naan</strong> onto a piece of foil</p><p>Add the <strong>crispy baharat basa </strong>down the middle of each naan, then top with some of the <strong>tomato salad </strong>and drizzle over the<strong> coriander mayo</strong></p><p>Fold the naan<strong> </strong>around the filling, widthways, using the tin foil to hold everything together<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>crispy baharat basa shawarma</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
