    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy baharat basa shawarma </strong>with the<strong> spiced potatoes</strong>, the <strong>remaining tomato salad </strong>and any <strong>remaining coriander mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
